# TypeScript Imports

Use **extensionless** import paths. Do NOT add `.js` (or `.ts`) suffixes to relative imports.

```typescript
// ❌ BAD
import { foo } from './foo.js'
import { bar } from '../utils/bar.js'

// ✅ GOOD
import { foo } from './foo'
import { bar } from '../utils/bar'
```

Project uses `moduleResolution: "bundler"` and tsx/tsc — extensionless paths resolve correctly.
